<br>
1) Innate taunt increase (similar to how my SK's Voice line buff does, but a smaller increase since it's permenant), I'd say about 2-3% max<br>
<br>
2) The enrage idea is a good one I think, but I think it should be a chance to enrage (or an ability you can only activate when low on health).  Yes, it's a LOT like the auto-riposte disc...except you can use this without messing with the discipline timer, which I would think would drastically increase the effectiveness.  You could even put ranks where each rank increased the duration of enrage.  (If not an AA, then a normal ability like /shield, but have AAs to increase duration, again like /shield.)<br>
<br>
3)  Not a point, but does the Flurry AA really not give a message to everyone when it goes off?  ****, you mean I've been looking all over for a warrior who has flurry so I can see it go off for nothing?  I want that fixed!  Nothing better than seeing a bold red message suddenly announcing your flurry...warriors look like big plush things otherwise, I swear.<br>
<br>
4)  AA to add a bit more agro than top+1 to the taunt ability<br>
<br>
5)  AA to lower taunt reuse by a couple seconds for warriors.<br>
<br>
6)  Slight innate chance to Death Pact yourself (call it a Guts ability) when about to die...that might be really powerful, now that I think about it.<br>
<br>
7) Chance to Crippling Blow without being beserk.<br>
<br>
Really I'd just like to see some of those disciplines come off the same timer, but that's just me. =P <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=3027.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showPrevMessage?topicID=3027.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showNextMessage?topicID=3027.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3027.topic&index=24><img src=http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/swaddreply.GIF border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.emailToFriend?topicID=3027.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.threadControl?topicID=3027.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3027.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3027.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub14.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesteelwar